## Commercial License (Paid)

A Commercial License is REQUIRED if:

1. Your organization has €100,000 or more in annual revenue
2. You want to offer CodeHero as a service to others
3. You want to remove CodeHero branding (white-label)
4. You want to integrate CodeHero into a commercial product

### Commercial License includes:

- Full rights to use in production environments
- Priority email support
- Access to future updates
- Optional: Custom feature development
- Optional: On-premise installation support
- Optional: White-label rights

### Pricing

Contact us for commercial licensing:

- **Email**: info@routeplanner.gr
- **Website**: https://routeplanner.gr/en/

